import {Grid,CardContent,Box,Typography} from '@material-ui/core'
import Countup from 'react-countup'


const Card=({cardTitle,value,desc,lastUpdate})=>{
    return (
        <Grid components>
            <Box>
                <Typography varient="h5" color='textSecondary'>{cardTitle}</Typography>
            </Box>
            <CardContent>
                <Typography varient="h5">
                    <Countup start={0} end={value} duration={3}seperator=","/>
                </Typography>
                <Typography>{desc}</Typography>
                <Typography>{new Date(lastUpdate).toDateString()}</Typography>
            </CardContent>
        </Grid>
    )
}
export default Card
